 Not to mention it's spectacular animation, from 2 titans fighting to the death or zip wiring from building to building like Spiderman, it's animation is leaps and bounds ahead of any other anime that's for sure. Mix this with an excellent soundtrack and you've got some of the most entertaining moments in anime.\
