With regards to major complications faced by our heroes, the first major battle boiled down to fighting a bunch of mindless monsters and then plugging up a hole in wall rose with a rock. Again, while enjoyable, the plot cannot be praised for being full of creativity. There are however several moments in the show which I felt were clever:\
